{
  "name": "[APEX] 01 - Client Document Collection & Chasing",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## [APEX] 01 - Client Document Collection & Chasing\n\n**Purpose:** When a job reaches 'awaiting client documents' status, send the client a document request email, then escalating reminders at Day 3, Day 7, and Day 14 if documents haven't been uploaded. All activity logged to Airtable.\n\n**Trigger:** POST to /webhook/doc-collection-start\n\n**Payload:** `{ clientId, clientName, clientEmail, engagementType, jobId, documentsRequired[] }`\n\n**Credentials to swap before activating:**\n- `AIRTABLE_CRED_ID` → Airtable Personal Access Token\n- `GMAIL_CRED_ID` → Gmail OAuth2\n\n**Placeholders to replace:**\n- `{{AIRTABLE_BASE_ID}}` → Your Airtable base ID\n- `{{UPLOAD_LINK}}` → Document upload portal URL\n- `{{PARTNER_EMAIL}}` → Engagement partner email",
        "height": 628,
        "width": 680,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "sticky-01",
      "name": "Workflow Info",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        176,
        80
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "doc-collection-start",
        "responseMode": "lastNode",
        "options": {}
      },
